---
title: Bulgogi Chicken Stir-Fry with Noodles, Green Beans and Peanuts
description: This Bulgogi Chicken Stir-Fry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220927_R01_W45_UK_F10137-16_MB_Main_low-9d44563d.jpg
